    <note>Sun(1) Tingchen [21372] Piling zhi, 11.9b; Wang Zao, WJ, 28.23a-26a (wife, born Shi(2), who died in 1148 at age 94). According to born Shi(2)'s funerary inscription, the family all lived together in a compound housing at least 15 sons and daughters and more than 60 grandchildren, great grandchildren and great great grandchildren--5 generations all living together. The Southeast shi dafu all used her as a model for the education of children and the management of the family. From the founding of the dynasty, more than 200 years, there have been seen only one or two like born Shi(2).</note>
